  "prompt": "What hotel in Etawah would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "Finding a hotel in Etawah (or any small town in India) that is safe and welcoming for unmarried couples can be a challenge due to societal norms and local regulations. However, here are some tips to ensure a safer and hassle-free stay:\n\n1. **Choose Reputed Hotels or Chains**: Opt for well-known hotel chains or higher-end hotels, as they are more likely to follow professional standards and respect guest privacy. While Etawah may not have many international chains, look for reputable local options.\n\n2. **Check Reviews**: Platforms like **Goibibo**, **MakeMyTrip**, or **Booking.com** often have reviews from guests, including couples. Look for mentions of \"couple-friendly\" or \"hassle-free check-in.\"\n\n3. **Book Online**: Use online booking platforms to avoid awkward conversations at the reception. Some platforms explicitly label hotels as \"couple-friendly.\"\n\n4. **Carry Valid IDs**: Both partners should carry valid government-issued IDs (Aadhar, PAN, passport, etc.) to avoid unnecessary scrutiny.\n\n5. **Be Confident and Discreet**: Avoid drawing unnecessary attention. Act confidently during check-in, as hesitation can sometimes lead to questioning.\n\n6. **Avoid Budget Hotels**: Budget hotels or lodges in smaller towns are more likely to follow conservative norms and may cause trouble.\n\n7. **Use Apps Like StayUncle or OYO**: Apps like **StayUncle** specialize in couple-friendly stays. While their presence in Etawah may be limited, it\u2019s worth checking. **OYO** also has some couple-friendly options, but be sure to read reviews.\n\n8. **Contact the Hotel Directly**: Before booking, call the hotel and ask about their policy for unmarried couples. Some hotels may explicitly state they are couple-friendly.\n\nIn Etawah, some options to consider (after verifying reviews and policies) include:\n\n- **Hotel Metro Palace**\n- **Hotel Krishna Continental**\n- **Hotel Kajal Residency**\n\nAlways double-check recent reviews and confirm with the hotel directly to ensure a smooth experience.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
